verbose_text: The expression of CNPase exhibited a significant increase in the rats that underwent treadmill training and EA, except in the rats treated with CEA alone compared to the HI group rats, and a significantly higher expression was also observed in the rats treated with SEA alone or co-treated (treadmill training and SEA) compared to the rats that underwent treadmill training alone (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG).
